bilingual.source: This recipe is only for four, so I usually do double the quantity if I'm cooking for my family.
bilingual.target: 这个食谱只适合四个人，所以如果我为家人做饭，我通常会做两倍的量。
两倍的泡泡糖能吹出两倍大的泡泡。

bilingual.source: I bought double the amount of milk.
Make mine a double scotch, straight up.
bilingual.target: 给我一杯两倍的直接压火酒。

bilingual.source: Steve: Make mine a double scotch, straight up.
bilingual.target: 给我一杯两倍的直接压火酒。

bilingual.source: Steve : Make mine a double scotch, straight up.
bilingual.target: 给我一杯两倍的直接压火酒.

bilingual.source: "You should pay me double the tuition fees," said Socrates.
bilingual.target: “你应该付给我两倍的学费，”苏格拉底说。

bilingual.source: The cunning businesswoman sold the house for double its value.
bilingual.target: 这个精明的女商人以实际价值两倍的价钱卖掉了这座房子。

bilingual.source: And the railroad, pardon the expression, caught h, e, double toothpicks.
bilingual.target: 以及重建公路干线乃至通往城里的公路。而铁路的修缮工作需要两倍的工作量。

list.abstract: double，英文单词，可作形容词、动词、副词、名词，翻译为两倍的、双人用的、使加倍、快步走、两倍等。
《Double》是由Tomato Fantasy Games制作的一款动作类通关战斗游戏。

yingyinNormal.en: What word? Blaba double. Blaba double. Right, you're in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是什么暗号。布拉达八卜，布拉达八卜。没错，你加入了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey! I ordered a double Krabby Patty!
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂！我可点了两份蟹黄堡！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: Just double-check your seat belts, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请再次检查安全带是否系好。

yingyinNormal.en: Grande double soy latte. Got it, Max? Nope.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中杯双份豆奶拿铁，听到了吗 Max？没呢。

yingyinNormal.en: I've double my battery life, by scavenging Rover 1.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通过搜刮1号车，我把电量增加了一倍。

yingyinNormal.en: Then double the amount of floggings and executions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把鞭刑和处决的数目加到双倍。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon. Double bazinga! I do! Good luck following that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿。还是逗你玩，我希望你好。要跟上哥的思维，你得加油啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Told you we should have double-checked the Western Reaches.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我跟你说过我们应该再搜索一遍西境。

yingyinNormal.en: I've been pulling double shifts for four months now, Chris.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经上双份班四个月了!

yingyinNormal.en: Double potion, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麻烦给我来双份。

yingyinNormal.en: You're supposed to double the tax. Not double the tax of Romania.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把税乘以二，不是把罗马尼亚的税收乘以二。

yingyinNormal.en: Grande double cap, non-fat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一杯中杯双份卡布奇诺，脱脂奶。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm thinking double wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 双重婚礼有戏了。

yingyinNormal.en: Great. How many does that make? High double digits. The nineties? Mid double digits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 厉害。现在有多少粉了？两位数高段班。90多粉丝啦？两位数中段班。

yingyinNormal.en: Zeng! Fly to OhorhGom prison and tell them to double the guards, double their weapons, double everything! Tai Lung does not leave that prison! Yes, Master Shifu!
yingyinNormal.zh: 老单，火速赶去乔岗大牢，要他们狱卒加倍，武器加倍，把一切都加倍，决不能让太狼逃出来。是，师父。

yingyinNormal.en: How come you never invite Sheldon and me on a double date?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么从来不邀请谢尔顿和我参加四人约会呢？

yingyinNormal.en: You are aware that a double date doesn't count as two dates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道双重约会不能抵两次约会的吧。

yingyinNormal.en: She says I need to be on Xanax and double my dose of Zoloft.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她让我吃点赞安诺，左洛复剂量加倍。

yingyinNormal.en: Ligature marks. Legs, arms. a double set of marks on her neck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 绳索痕迹，腿上有，胳膊上有，脖子上有两道。

yingyinNormal.en: He says he's gonna double the college money my Grandma left me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说可以把祖母留给我的大学学费再增加一倍。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The percentage of retirement-age people in the labor force has <highlight>doubled</highlight> over the past three decades.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在过去30年里，退休年龄人群在劳动力中的比例翻了一番。

examination_example.sentence: In many countries of Western Europe the numbers of students in higher education <highlight>doubled</highlight> within five-year periods.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在许多西欧国家，接受高等教育的学生人数在五年内翻了一番。

examination_example.sentence: Starting around 2012, requests for the visas rose sharply; from 2011 to 2016 the number of visas issued more than <highlight>doubled</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从2012年左右开始，申请签证的人数急剧增加；从2011年到2016年，签发的签证数量翻了一番多。

examination_example.sentence: Today, 28 per cent of graduates in the UK are in non-graduate roles, a percentage which is <highlight>double</highlight> the average among OECD countries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如今，英国28%的毕业生从事非毕业生工作，这一比例是经合组织国家平均水平的两倍。

examination_example.sentence: The state's proposed Forest Carbon Plan aims to <highlight>double</highlight> efforts to thin out young trees and clear brush in parts of the forest.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该州提出的森林碳计划旨在加倍努力减少小树和清除部分森林中的灌木丛。

examination_example.sentence: Rather officials must avoid <highlight>double</highlight> standards, or different types of access for average people and the wealthy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，官员们必须避免双重标准，或者对普通人和富人采取不同的准入方式。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: According to official statistics, Thailand's annual road-death rate is almost <highlight>double</highlight> the global average.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据官方统计，泰国每年的道路死亡率几乎是全球平均水平的两倍。

examination_example.sentence: It is estimated that to meet the 2050 challenge, investment must <highlight>double</highlight> to 83 billion US dollars a year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 据估计，为了迎接2050年的挑战，投资必须翻一番，达到每年830亿美元。

examination_example.sentence: Meanwhile, the world's population more than <highlight>doubled</highlight> from 3 billion between 1961 and 2007.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，从1961年到2007年，世界人口从30亿增加了一倍多。

examination_example.sentence: The tendency is often to <highlight>double</highlight> down on their current position rather than publicly admit to being wrong.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们往往会加倍坚持目前的立场，而不是公开承认自己错了。

sense_info_list.en: to have another use or function as well as the main one

examination_example.sentence: We should consider it as a tool for seeing and understanding the world better—one that just so happens to <highlight>double</highlight> as an art form.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们应该把绘画看作是一种更好地观察和理解世界的工具——一种恰好同时作为一种艺术形式的工具。

sense_info_list.en: an actor who replaces another actor in a film/movie to do dangerous or other special things

examination_example.sentence: Framestore used body <highlight>doubles</highlight> with resemblance to Hepburn's facial structure and body shape as a framework for manual animation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Framestore使用与Hepburn面部结构和体型相似的身体替身作为手绘动画的框架。

word_usage.usage:
double用作形容词的基本意思是“双的”，其所修饰的名词一般为单数。
This machine serves a double purpose.
这部机器有双重用途。

examination_example.sentence: But others do <highlight>double</highlight> duty.

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Diabetes <highlight>doubles</highlight> a person's risk of early death.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 糖尿病使人早逝的风险增加了一倍。

examination_example.sentence: Because of him, my English scores <highlight>doubled</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为他，我的英语成绩提高了一倍。

examination_example.sentence: You might be surprised to hear that the number of people sleeping rough(露宿)has <highlight>doubled</highlight> in the last five years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 听到露宿街头的人数在过去五年翻了一番，你可能会感到惊讶。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>Double</highlight> Ninth Festival is a special day for older people in China.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对中国的老年人来说，重阳节是一个特殊的节日。

examination_example.sentence: When is the <highlight>Double</highlight> Ninth Festival?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 重阳节是在什么时候？

examination_example.sentence: The Chongyang Festival falls on the ninth day of the ninth lunar month and is called the <highlight>Double</highlight> Ninth Festival.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 重阳节在农历九月初九，亦被称为九九重阳节。
